title: San Francisco Maritime National Historical Park: Sounds From Around the Park
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia     Multimedia Presentations     Sounds From Around the Park                Sounds From Around the Park              Early Morning Summer Sounds     Early morning summer sounds of gentle waves washing over rocks at Aquatic Park beach. This was recorded on World Listening Day, July 18, 2013.  Duration:1 minute, 5 seconds      Credit / Author: NPS, Kristal Ip   Date created: 2013-07-18                     Baby Gulls on Aquatic Park Beach     Sounds of baby gulls on Aquatic Park beach.  Duration:32 seconds      Credit / Author: NPS, Kristal Ip   Date created: 2013-08-08                     Sounds From a Typical Thursday Morning     Sounds recorded on the Bathhouse building veranda that overlooks Aquatic Park beach and San Francisco Bay. Someone was playing the piano in the Senior Center located at the east end of the veranda.  Duration:50 seconds      Credit / Author: NPS, Kristal Ip   Date created: 2013-08-22                The audio file listed above, Early Morning Summer Sounds, was recorded here. NPS Photo
